  $T$kb-doc/system-standards/system-diagram$T$,
  $T${"blocks":[{"type":"Hero","props":{"lede":"Single-image overview of the dashboard system. Sidebar spine, three render paths, data layer, four standards docs, four session hooks, MCP tools, voice stack. Regenerated 2026-05-13 with Gemini Nano Banana v2 — exact strings, no hallucinations, color-coded lanes.","title":"MyJarvis Dashboard — System Map","eyebrow":"SYSTEM · DIAGRAM"}},{"type":"ImageBlock","props":{"alt":"MyJarvis Dashboard system architecture diagram","src":"https://{{r2_public_host}}/assets/system-diagram-v2-20260513-142617.png","caption":"*Generated 2026-05-13 with Gemini 2.5 Flash Image (Nano Banana) v2. Color-coded lanes — sky-blue domains, three render-path columns, amber data layer, stone-gray hooks + standards, violet voice stack. Exact strings — no hallucinations.*"}},{"type":"Divider","props":{}},{"type":"SectionHeader","props":{"title":"Where the contract lives","eyebrow":"01 — WHAT TO READ NEXT"}},{"type":"P","props":{"body":"This page is a visual companion to the dashboard skill. For the full operating spec, read these three docs in this order:"}},{"type":"DataTable","props":{"rows":[["**Dashboard skill**","Neon `skills.body` for slug `dashboard` (`skill://dashboard`)","Required before any dashboard write"],["**`/dashboard-architecture`**","Neon `page_content` for `kb-doc/mj-os/dashboard-architecture`","Browsable companion — same content as skill"],["**`CLAUDE.md`**","`/Users/{{operator_handle}}/Workspace/jarvis-pai/CLAUDE.md`","Workspace contract — high-level rules"],["**MCP `INSTRUCTIONS`**","`my-jarvis-mcp/src/index.ts`","Enforces skill reading"]],"headers":["Doc","Where","When to read"]}},{"type":"Divider","props":{}},{"type":"SectionHeader","props":{"title":"Three render paths, locked","eyebrow":"02 — THE STANDARD"}},{"type":"Grid3","props":{"cards":[{"h4":"Structured","body":"Bespoke React + `useApi()`. Lists, kanban, dashboards, forms, indexes.","h4ColorToken":"skyDark"},{"h4":"Knowledge — Classic","body":"`<BlockRenderer config={architectureConfig}>`. Editorial + detail pages of structured rows.","h4ColorToken":"green"},{"h4":"Knowledge — Pitch deck","body":"`<BlockRenderer config={pitchDeckConfig}>`. Slide-deck experiences.","h4ColorToken":"violet"}]}},{"type":"Divider","props":{}},{"type":"SectionHeader","props":{"title":"See the whole picture","eyebrow":"XX — CROSS-LINKS"}},{"type":"P","props":{"body":"**Sister diagrams in the standards set:** [System Architecture](/kb-doc/mj-os/system-diagram) · [Data Flows](/kb-doc/mj-os/data-flows) · [Operating Model](/kb-doc/mj-os/operating-model) · [Knowledge Taxonomy](/kb-doc/mj-os/knowledge-taxonomy) · [Persona Stack](/kb-doc/mj-os/persona-stack)."}},{"type":"Footer","props":{"line1":"System diagram — locked 2026-05-13. Regenerate with the same Nano Banana prompt if the system shape changes.","line2":"For prompt + script, see ticket MJOS-054 work log."}}]}$T$::jsonb
)
